title: Tunisia: Launch of Tunisia-Africa Business Council
text:
Zimbabwe: Mining Requires U.S $4 Billion to Ramp Up Output Tunis — The Tunisia-Africa Business Council was launched Friday in Tunis to boost economic co-operation and promote relations between Tunisian and African investors. The council launch ceremony was held on the occasion with the participation of several ambassadors of African countries to Tunisia. Tunisia
